Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for shoving others aside and volunteering to come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Flatt and Svin are on extracurricular lessons anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to be very careful while you're on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a dangerous train?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rail Zeppelin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a train that superhuman vampires created
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to make deals with Mystic Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Its existence itself is equal to that of the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that one of those customers is the culprit who stole the relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they aren't,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,only supernatural beings would board this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:00:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you brought glasses that eradicate Mystic Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You really make good preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashino Hishiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I expected you to be on the move based on the materials concerning Wills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking some Lord was here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't expect the rumored Modern Magecraft Theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a while, Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the figurehead of Norwich recognizes my face at the least?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Olga-Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Olga-Marie Arsimilat Animusphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the daughter of the Lord of Astromancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you have some particular Mystic Eyes you're after?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make this clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but Astromancy will make sure to win this year's auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm up against a Lord, I'm not going to go easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you overestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Trisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I ask you one thing. Don't get in the way of Animusphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So scary, so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unusual for an Animusphere to descend from the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural for Astromancy to show interest in Mystic Eyes that can predict the Mystics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:27.04,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:56.34,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this place is larger than it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This train itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But they sure are all notable figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know the faces of half of them,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but they're all monsters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Karabo Frampton...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Holy Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! The Holy Church came out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that contends against the Clock Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it. I don't mean to stir up any trouble here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to participate in the auction, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you object?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that reaction was to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Professor El-Melloi II is here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yvette! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My family is an authority of Mystic Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're regulars of the auction on the Mystic Eyes Collection Train! It's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I didn't expect Caules to be here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you one of his sycophants?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, though it's true that I asked him to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, it's not good to be cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, maybe BL can be a thing?\NI'm sorry if I'm not good with multiplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be his mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm a regular at sneaking into the bedroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, jump out of that window right this second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon the interruption of your pleasant chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Leandra, and I'll be the auctioneer for this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm Rodin, the conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, Rail Zeppelin will be departing as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The auction in three days' time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,will have many prized Mystic Eyes\Nfrom our collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make sure to spend your time here with no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who invited me never showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go look for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it. Something will surely happen now that I've been lured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no good in simply worrying under our current conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was up all night last night, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Shishigou Kairi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd be called over to a fancy place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, I can't imagine that it would suit your palette, Lady Reines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a place my elder brother patronizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, they serve delicious sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what does the little sister of a Lord want with a freelance magician like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother's catalyst for the Holy Grail War has been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't mean the ritual utensil to summon a Heroic Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:08:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What was stolen is the mantle of Iskandar, King of Conquerors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite an item to bring out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was something that Kayneth specially obtained.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The mantle of the King of Conquerors...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,could create a magical bond with Iskandar or one of his subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something any Necromancer would like to get his hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My elder brother has boarded the Mystic Eyes\NCollection Train in order to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you can't be telling me to go back him up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Apparently, it's absolutely impossible to board that train without an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What I need are clues about the perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So, playing detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about investigating a perpetrator who can steal a catalyst from a Lord's vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I need someone who can deal with things getting a bit rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what you're getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But why aren't you resolving this within Modern Magecraft Theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's because I suspect someone on the inside the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that how it goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I'll give you an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A reliable one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, little apprentice! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you take this plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you order something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. I'm not feeling too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's something like him asking for five more minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's not a good riser, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Five more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You really know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I want to be his mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"A mistress," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not fazed by this comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're not a rival, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mystic Eyes of Viewing Emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My family's magecraft cuts gems and turns them into Mystic Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This one can see human emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What comment should I have been fazed by?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't worth my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yvette...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, come on over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cute apprentice is here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the conductor about who sent us the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it was one of the free slot invitations that are handed out to several people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know who originally had this invitation, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a few free slot invites are sent out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don't invite new people, the auction becomes too routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be over a dozen of those sent out every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we won't be able to trace them through the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,More like you could've asked me instead of Caules
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,if it was something about this train!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why I didn't do so will be the topic for your self-study!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cruel! You're so mean, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please bait them out well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This was wedged into the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"I am honored that you noticed the invitation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and made your way out here."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's from that thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They want me to head to the cargo bay at twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord El-Melloi II?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I speak with you for a short while?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can speak of anything that would win your favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't quite say that I'm a customer for this auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel you're the most suited person in the Clock Tower to talk about this with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's about the Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Astromancy want to do with the Holy Grail War?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How the previous El-Melloi passed away
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,was discussed over at Animusphere, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's so talked about that you hear of it even if you're a shut-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How you want to join the Holy Grail War even by mobilizing the Sophia-Ri family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think Animusphere would be that interested in the ordinary world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a fragment of a planet, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at the heavens and looking at Earth are the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Observing the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We concluded that you came here to purchase Mystic Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as a weapon to use in the Holy Grail War.\NAre we mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not exactly correct, I guess you could say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want is the eye-catcher of this auction, Rainbow Mystic Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Mystic Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate operation of celestial bodies within the human body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not well-versed, but is it something that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Each Mystic Eyes has a rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher caliber Mystic Eyes are ranked as "Gold-class," then "Jewel-class,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and "Rainbow-class" is a rank above those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it actually existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe almost no one at the Clock Tower\Nhas seen Rainbow Mystic Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But if such Mystic Eyes are going to be put up for auction,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't you think that I'd purchase it for the Holy Grail War?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think El-Melloi in its current state has that much financial prowess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are blunt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So, you're certain there'll be Rainbow Mystic Eyes at the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, Trisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The talk will go smoother if we show at least that card to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord El-Melloi II,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,can you raise your right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I need to head outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mystic Eyes of Premonition, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a vision where Rainbow Mystic Eyes were put up for auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Rainbow Mystic Eyes come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to bid if some other fool were to bid for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You were the one who told me I don't have the fortune to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No magus would be foolish enough to antagonize two families of Lords, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can fold as soon as the others do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can curb the damage to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I'll comply with your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It helps me out that you can have constructive conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a suitable reward if you assist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I'm slightly motion sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this train doesn't run along typical railroad tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mystic Eyes Collection Train runs along magical tracks built atop leylines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not used to it, your condition will worsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some sugar and hydrate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That should make things slightly better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no intent of looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So, you're not a magus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The guise of King Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the past with my Mystic Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to see such things, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said, I'm not a magus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I call myself "Master's Apprentice," but that's only in name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're unsure of whether or not you're of any use to the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fine. You're already someone he finds necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that magecraft, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what you call "life experience."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,May I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When we did our research about the previous Holy Grail War,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we got to know about a boy named Waver Velvet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that a terrible record to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He was only a third-generation magus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He was far from what you could call promising,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but he returned alive from the Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However, upon return,\Nhe was resolved to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and succeeded the El-Melloi family,\Nnow being called a "Lord."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Only in name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That must mean the Holy Grail War was a large turning point in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,meeting a hero of yore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,An interesting speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,one more to add to speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to summon the same Heroic Spirit once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't the Servant have no memories
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of racing through this world with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that Astromancy was interested in things as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That definitely is something that has nothing to do with the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that connections are similar to stars, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like to ask myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of Rainbow Mystic Eyes did you folks have a vision of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe we have no need to tell you that much in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter which Mystic Eyes Collection Train you're on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot imagine them being able to ready two sets of Rainbow-class Mystic Eyes at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, that is reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans live being dependent on information,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and they die being bound by information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of which, vision provides the largest amount of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Vision is the first magecraft in human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To incorporate information can be said as the foundation of magecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why humans are dominated by memories, by information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:20:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To have Mystic Eyes is to accept the destiny of being bound by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are going to purchase Mystic Eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,please take that into careful consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm greatly obliged by your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This train will stop at this location for about two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You are free to spend this time either aboard the train or wandering outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard something about myself and the Holy Grail War?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Servants don't have memories of previous summons, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That was something I've understood for the longest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But Master, if there is someone you are devoted to,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting that person to have memories of you is only natural, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. It's not like I don't care whether or not he has forgotten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's someone I want to meet despite all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something I want to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something to settle and finish
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can walk past the last ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm fixated on just that, something so petty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of us being remembered
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and being able to relish each other's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Such happiness is too big a reward even if it was deferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly pay that off in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just getting a breath of forest air.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:21:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,when I returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Trisha...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Trisha was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:10.10,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
